<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <title>Dashboard</title>
    <%- include('../../partials/head.ejs') %>
        <link rel='stylesheet' href='/stylesheets/style.css' />
</head>

<body class="bg-white">
    <%- include('../../partials/nav.ejs') %>
        <%- include('../../partials/topNav.ejs') %>

            <div class="mt-6 md:mt-0 md:ml-64">
                <div class="md:py-8 mx-5 sm:mx-8 lg:mx-14 xl:mx-20">
                    <div class="py-6 lg:py-10 bg-white lg:border">

                        <div class="mx-5 lg:px-6">
                            <div>
                                <img class="w-32" src="/assets/images/CSR-A_Logo-RGB.jpg" alt="logo" />
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="mx-5 lg:px-6 pb-5 text-justify text-sm lg:text-base">
                            <div class="pt-8">
                                <h3 class="font-bold text-lg">GENERAL INTRODUCTION</h3>

                                <p class="pt-2">
                                    An overview of your environmental and socially responsible strategy. Your General Introduction should highlight key
                                    policies, initiatives, impacts and achievements which you should describe in greater detail in the subsequent Four
                                    Pillars sections. (We are looking for no more than a few paragraphs for your General Introduction).
                                </p>
                            </div>

                            <form class="pt-5">
                                <textarea id="introduction_textarea" placeholder="Text..." class="p-8 max-h-96 text-justify resize-y h-40 w-full border border-[#464343]"></textarea>
                            </form>
                        </div>

                        <div class="text-right text-sm mt-3 text-white pr-5 lg:pr-10">
                            <button id="submit_btn" onclick="updateApplicationIntroduction()" class="py-2 px-3 hover:bg-[#03857e] w-32 rounded-md shadow-lg bg-[#00A19A] transition ease-in-out delay-150 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:scale-110 hover:animate-none animate-bounce duration-300">Save</button>
                        </div>
                    <p class="mt-5 font-bold pl-5 text-red-700">
                        AS A MINIMUM REQUIREMENT, WE EXPECT ALL APPLICANTS TO FOLLOW STATUTORY REQUIREMENTS AND TO MEET ALL RELEVANT
                        NATIONAL
                        AND INTERNATIONAL LEGISLATION.
                    </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <script defer src="https://unpkg.com/alpinejs@3.10.2/dist/cdn.min.js"></script>
            </script>
            <script src="/javascripts/others/application_introduction.js"></script>
</body>

</html>